A3: (for p being Real holds ((( 0 ) < p & p < 1) implies (for t,s being Real holds ((((t in X & s in X) & ( ( p * t ) + ( ( 1 - p ) * s ) ) in X) & t <> s) implies ( ( f - r ) . ( ( p * t ) + ( ( 1 - p ) * s ) ) ) < ( ( p * ( ( f - r ) . t ) ) + ( ( 1 - p ) * ( ( f - r ) . s ) ) )))))
